Re-installing the app typically solves most technical issues. If your problem persists, please contact us at support@coinidentifierai.com.
How do I change my payment method?

Easily manage your payment method in your phone’s settings. Please follow the instructions below:\niOS: https://support.apple.com/HT201266\nAndroid: https://support.google.com/googleplay/answer/4646404
How do I know if I have CoinSnap Premium or the free version?

To check, follow these steps:
1. Go to the "Me" page
2. Tap the "Settings" icon in the upper right corner
3. You’ll see your premium membership status under "My Premium Service". If your account says "Premium Membership", it means you have the premium version. Otherwise, you’ll see that you’re in the free mode.
How can I delete my account and all data?
How to restore my Premium membership on a new device?

If you have an active subscription to CoinSnap Premium, "Restore Purchase" helps you regain access:
1. Make sure that you’re logged in with the same credentials you used to subscribe
2. Launch the CoinSnap app
3. Tap "Services" on the homepage
4. Tap "Restore" at the top left of the subscription offer page

Yes, we are cautious about sharing personal information. Although the app requires access to your photo gallery, we never process or share any photos without your permission, nor do we share your information with anyone.
What are the benefits of CoinSnap Premium?

CoinSnap Premium offers you the following benefits: 
- Unlimited coin identifications
- Consultation with coin experts
- A rich database of content on thousands of coins
- Exclusive support team at your fingertips
- No ads or watermarks
How do I save a photo in the app?
Manually save any photo by tapping the photo on the details page and long press.
How do I share my identification with friends?

Simply follow the instructions below:
1. Launch the app then navigate to the "Me" section
2. Tap the coin picture you want to share
3. Tap "Share" on the top right of the screen
4. Select a channel to export your identification
Can subscriptions be set up to automatically renew?

Yes, when you purchase a CoinSnap Premium, your subscription will automatically renew either monthly or annually (depending on your purchase term).
